âœ… 2ï¸âƒ£ UML SEQUENCE DIAGRAM â€“ Approval Routing

This shows interaction flow clearly.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Maker
    actor Checker
    actor AltChecker
    actor Controller
    participant System

    Maker->>System: Submit Plan
    System->>Checker: Notify Plan Pending

    Checker->>System: Approve / Reject

    alt Rejected by Checker
        System->>Maker: Return as Draft with Comments
    else Approved by Checker
        System->>AltChecker: Forward Plan
    end

    AltChecker->>System: Approve / Reject

    alt Rejected by AltChecker
        System->>Maker: Return as Draft
    else Approved
        System->>Controller: Forward Plan
    end

    Controller->>System: Final Approval / Reject

    alt Rejected by Controller
        System->>Maker: Return as Draft
    else Approved
        System->>Maker: Plan Approved Successfully
    end


